'''''The Changing Dream''''' is the book that was written by the former [[United States Senate|United States Senator]] and [[United States House of Representatives|Representative]] [[John V. Tunney]], who was the son of the 1926 to 1928 heavyweight [[boxing]] champion, [[Gene Tunney]].

The subtitle is ''The Truth About the Material and Energy Crisis and What We Must Do to Resolve It.''

[[Doubleday (publisher)|Doubleday & Company, Inc.]], [[Garden City, New York]], 1975.  {{ISBN|0-385-04850-5}}

